				<td colspan="2"><span>Hi all, please help me understand the deal.  I just bought the Troubadors Mace and it has percussion instrument on it.  What does this mean?  Does this take the place of my drum, so if I were running selos with the troub mace in hand, will I go at Walrus Skin Drum speed or Thunderous Drum of Karana Speed?  Do I still need to equip the drum or what?  What is the instrument property of the Troub mace and other weapons do for you? Thanks in advance.</span></td>
