<br />

<br />
The best way to get your instrument skill up is to park your self somewhere where you won't get run over by a wandering monster or guard, take out the instrument and play!  Go to bed or work (p'tooie) or whatever and come back in a few hours.  (It helps to get a few stacks of food and drink, but isn't really necessary.)  Like all musicians, we bards have to practice, practice, practice.  I usually put up an AFK message like &quot;instrument practice&quot; to be polite, and have at it.
<br />

<br />

<br />

